# Runtime/test logs: the spd file sink and proto log write under logsDir, which Settings::Load sets to
# <cwd>/logs - so any run with a cwd inside the repo drops them in-tree.
# Deliberately not a bare "logs/": that would also match web/framework/control/src/lib/pages/logs, which is source.
*.log
/logs/
